  "description": "The drop has happened. The aftershock phase — stripped back, disorienting, before the second build. Minimal four-on-the-floor with doumbek ghost notes that feel like the reverb of the drop still ringing. Beatbox snare comes in only on beat 3, not 2+4 — an asymmetric tension machine. GATHER from 0 to 1.0 brings in the rebuild wave.",
